main event: Witness observed two to three unidentified objects moving in a straight line above the ground.
interesting points: The objects were about three feet in diameter and hovered several feet above the ground., The objects made no sound and had no lights or markings., The witness described the objects as moving rapidly and defying the laws of gravity., Multiple reports indicated frequent sightings of flying saucers in the area., The sighting raised questions regarding experimental aircraft.
sighted object: two to three unidentified flying objects
witness description: The witness saw the objects while driving on highway M-46.
